description: Creates a pull through cache rule. A pull through cache rule provides a way to cache images from an upstream registry source in your Amazon ECR private registry. For more information, see Using pull through cache rules in the Amazon Elastic Container Registry User Guide.

parameters.name: ecrRepositoryPrefix
parameters.description: The repository name prefix to use when caching images from the source registry.

parameters.name: upstreamRegistryUrl
parameters.description: The registry URL of the upstream public registry to use as the source for the pull through cache rule. The following is the syntax to use for each supported upstream registry. Amazon ECR ( ecr) --- dkr.ecr.<region>.amazonaws.com Amazon ECR Public ( ecr-public) --- public.ecr.aws Docker Hub ( docker-hub) --- registry-1.docker.io GitHub Container Registry ( github-container-registry) --- ghcr.io GitLab Container Registry ( gitlab-container-registry) --- registry.gitlab.com Kubernetes ( k8s) --- registry.k8s.io Microsoft Azure Container Registry ( azure-container-registry) --- <custom>.azurecr.io Quay ( quay) --- quay.io.

nested_items.name: ecrRepositoryPrefix
nested_items.description: The Amazon ECR repository prefix associated with the pull through cache rule.

nested_items.name: upstreamRegistryUrl
nested_items.description: The upstream registry URL associated with the pull through cache rule.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The date and time, in JavaScript date format, when the pull through cache rule was created.

nested_items.name: registryId
nested_items.description: The registry ID associated with the request.

nested_items.name: upstreamRegistry
nested_items.description: The name of the upstream registry associated with the pull through cache rule.

nested_items.name: credentialArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the Amazon Web Services Secrets Manager secret associated with the pull through cache rule.

nested_items.name: customRoleArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the IAM role associated with the pull through cache rule.

nested_items.name: upstreamRepositoryPrefix
nested_items.description: The upstream repository prefix associated with the pull through cache rule.
